{"id":171,"date":"2020-09-22T17:32:43","date_gmt":"2020-09-22T17:32:43","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost\/?p=171"},"modified":"2020-09-23T16:05:23","modified_gmt":"2020-09-23T16:05:23","slug":"iot-esp8266-04-doc-tin-hieu-bien-tro","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/localhost\/2020\/09\/22\/iot-esp8266-04-doc-tin-hieu-bien-tro\/","title":{"rendered":"IOT-ESP8266: 04-\u0110\u1ecdc t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u bi\u1ebfn tr\u1edf"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Tr\u00ean kit nodemcu c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n 1 ch\u00e2n ADC &#8211; Analog to digital conventer, gi\u00fap cho ch\u00fang ta d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ecdc c\u00e1c t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u analog t\u1eeb c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn, thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb,&#8230; <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ESP8266-analog-reading-read-ADC-A0-Arduino-IDE-MicroPython-Lua.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-172\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u00ean kit node mcu th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec7n \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o s\u1ebd t\u1eeb 0-&gt;3.3V, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chip esp8266 th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec7n \u00e1p ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 0-&gt;1V. Ngo\u00e0i ra b\u1ed9 ADC t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0 10bit n\u00ean ta s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u1eeb 0-&gt;1023(t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng 0 -&gt; 0V v\u00e0 1023 -&gt; 3.3V)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee9ng<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c kit c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n nh\u01b0 nodemcu,&#8230; th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111i\u1ec7n \u00e1p ph\u00e2n c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean bi\u1ebfn tr\u1edf\/chi\u1ebft \u00e1p v\u00e0o th\u1eb3ng ch\u00e2n A0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"458\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/analog_input_pot_esp8266_bb.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-175\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp chip esp8266 th\u00ec c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed1i qua c\u1ea7u ph\u00e2n \u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o chip<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"735\" height=\"622\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ESP8266-ADC-or-A0_bb.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-176\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u00fang ta s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 2 \u0111i\u1ec7n tr\u1edf 220 \u00f4m v\u00e0 100 \u00f4m, khi \u0111\u00f3 ta s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec7n \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"349\" height=\"97\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/voltage-divider-equation.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-177\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Code tham kh\u1ea3o<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"EnlighterJSRAW\" data-enlighter-language=\"generic\" data-enlighter-theme=\"\" data-enlighter-highlight=\"\" data-enlighter-linenumbers=\"\" data-enlighter-lineoffset=\"\" data-enlighter-title=\"\" data-enlighter-group=\"\">const int analogInPin = A0;  \/\/ ESP8266 Analog Pin ADC0 = A0\n\nint sensorValue = 0;  \/\/ value read from the pot\nint outputValue = 0;  \/\/ value to output to a PWM pin\n\nvoid setup() {\n  \/\/ initialize serial communication at 115200\n  Serial.begin(115200);\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  \/\/ read the analog in value\n  sensorValue = analogRead(analogInPin);\n  \n  \/\/ map it to the range of the PWM out\n  outputValue = map(sensorValue, 0, 1023, 0, 255);\n  \n  \/\/ print the readings in the Serial Monitor\n  Serial.print(\"sensor = \");\n  Serial.print(sensorValue);\n  Serial.print(\"\\t output = \");\n  Serial.println(outputValue);\n\n  delay(1000);\n}<\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \ud83d\ude00<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"744\" height=\"541\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ESP8266-Analog-Read-ADC-A0-Arduino-IDE-Serial-Monitor-Readingsf.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-178\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc li\u00ean h\u1ec7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp fanpage tr\u00ean facebook nh\u00e9<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Tr\u00ean kit nodemcu c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n 1 ch\u00e2n ADC &#8211; Analog to digital conventer, gi\u00fap cho ch\u00fang ta d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ecdc c\u00e1c t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u analog t\u1eeb [&hellip;] <span class=\"read-more-link\"><a class=\"read-more\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/2020\/09\/22\/iot-esp8266-04-doc-tin-hieu-bien-tro\/\">Xem th\u00eam<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":172,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[4],"tags":[6,12,15,16,7,8,9,10,11,13,14],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/171"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=171"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/171\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":182,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/171\/revisions\/182"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/172"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=171"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/w